keeping up with the &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 2016 american action comedy film directed by greg mottola and written by michael &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . starring zach galifianakis , jon hamm , isla fisher and gal gadot , the film follows a suburban couple ( galifianakis and fisher ) who begin to suspect their new neighbors ( hamm and gadot ) are secret agents . the film was released on october 21 , 2016 by 20th century fox , received generally negative reviews and was a box office bomb , grossing $ 29 million against its $ 40 million budget .